Package: LDZipMatrix
Type: Package
Title: Efficient Compression and Random Access for Linkage Disequilibrium Matrices
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-08-15
Author: Sayantan Das
Maintainer: Sayantan Das <sayantand@23andme.com>
Description: LDZipMatrix provides tools to compress, store, and access large-scale linkage disequilibrium (LD) matrices efficiently. It supports reading and writing compressed LD data with minimal storage overhead, while enabling fast random access from R through a C++ backend.
